          "range": "1246-1282",
          "rangeStart": 1246,
          "rangeEnd": 1282,
          "markText": "如果你只有一样东西，你当然要尽情夸耀它。也许拥有的越少，就越需要夸耀吧。",
          "colorStyle": 2,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1753923815,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-07-31 09:03:35",
          "chapterUid": 67,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300144647&chapterUid=67&rangeStart=1246&rangeEnd=1282",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fc332560813ab9f00g0174d0?chapterUid=67&rangeStart=1246&rangeEnd=1282"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300144647_5_2935-2981",
          "range": "2916-2962",
          "rangeStart": 2916,
          "rangeEnd": 2962,
          "markText": "干旱的年份，人们总忘记丰年，而多雨的年头，他们又失去了对旱年的所有记忆。从无例外，总是如此。",
          "colorStyle": 2,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1753923799,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-07-31 09:03:19",
          "chapterUid": 67,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300144647&chapterUid=67&rangeStart=2916&rangeEnd=2962",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fc332560813ab9f00g0174d0?chapterUid=67&rangeStart=2916&rangeEnd=2962"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300144647_5_565-656",
          "range": "548-639",
          "rangeStart": 548,
          "rangeEnd": 639,
          "markText": "我还记得儿时给草地和隐秘的花朵取的名字。我记得蟾蜍可能生活的地方，鸟儿在夏天醒来的时间，记得树木和季节的气息，记得人们的模样、走路的姿势，甚至是身上的味道。关于气味的记忆是那么丰富。",
          "colorStyle": 2,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1753923792,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-07-31 09:03:12",
          "chapterUid": 67,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300144647&chapterUid=67&rangeStart=548&rangeEnd=639",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fc332560813ab9f00g0174d0?chapterUid=67&rangeStart=548&rangeEnd=639"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
