    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300144647_69_2708-2742",
      "chapterUid": 69,
      "range": "2708-2742",
      "markText": "在那个时代，一个男人在普普通通的一生中，消耗三四个妻子是很正常的事。",
      "totalCount": 1590,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300144647&chapterUid=69&rangeStart=2708&rangeEnd=2742",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fc332560813ab9f00g0174d0?chapterUid=69&rangeStart=2708&rangeEnd=2742"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300144647_69_2584-2661",
      "chapterUid": 69,
      "range": "2584-2661",
      "markText": "塞勒斯想找个女人照顾亚当。他需要有人操持家务、洗衣做饭，而请用人是要花钱的。他是个精力旺盛的男人，需要女人的身体，而这也是要花钱的——除非你跟那女人结婚。",
      "totalCount": 1456,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300144647&chapterUid=69&rangeStart=2584&rangeEnd=2661",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fc332560813ab9f00g0174d0?chapterUid=69&rangeStart=2584&rangeEnd=2661"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300144647_125_19674-19696",
      "chapterUid": 125,
      "range": "19674-19696",
      "markText": "“愿上帝保佑您健康——希望他也不要忘了我。”",
      "totalCount": 1424,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300144647&chapterUid=125&rangeStart=19674&rangeEnd=19696",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fc332560813ab9f00g0174d0?chapterUid=125&rangeStart=19674&rangeEnd=19696"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300144647_67_548-639",
      "chapterUid": 67,
      "range": "548-639",
      "markText": "我还记得儿时给草地和隐秘的花朵取的名字。我记得蟾蜍可能生活的地方，鸟儿在夏天醒来的时间，记得树木和季节的气息，记得人们的模样、走路的姿势，甚至是身上的味道。关于气味的记忆是那么丰富。",
      "totalCount": 1392,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300144647&chapterUid=67&rangeStart=548&rangeEnd=639",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fc332560813ab9f00g0174d0?chapterUid=67&rangeStart=548&rangeEnd=639"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300144647_68_2681-2752",
      "chapterUid": 68,
      "range": "2681-2752",
      "markText": "他们都叫他喜剧天才，把他讲的故事小心翼翼地带回家，可他们想知道这些故事是怎么在路上漏掉的，因为等他们在自家厨房里再次讲起时，听起来就不一样了。",
      "totalCount": 1280,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300144647&chapterUid=68&rangeStart=2681&rangeEnd=2752",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fc332560813ab9f00g0174d0?chapterUid=68&rangeStart=2681&rangeEnd=2752"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300144647_104_4867-4963",
      "chapterUid": 104,
      "range": "4867-4963",
      "markText": "老李把酒瓶举到嘴边，喝了一大口热辣辣的烈酒，从仿佛燃烧着的喉咙里喷出酒气。“亚当，”他说，“我回来太高兴了，从没有这么高兴过，难以置信的高兴，无法控制的高兴。我这辈子他妈的从没有那么孤单过。”",
      "totalCount": 1105,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300144647&chapterUid=104&rangeStart=4867&rangeEnd=4963",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fc332560813ab9f00g0174d0?chapterUid=104&rangeStart=4867&rangeEnd=4963"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300144647_65_446-480",
      "chapterUid": 65,
      "range": "446-480",
      "markText": "上次看到我用木头雕刻小人像的时候，你说：“你怎么不给我做点东西呢？”",
      "totalCount": 884,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300144647&chapterUid=65&rangeStart=446&rangeEnd=480",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fc332560813ab9f00g0174d0?chapterUid=65&rangeStart=446&rangeEnd=480"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300144647_71_1465-1561",
      "chapterUid": 71,
      "range": "1465-1561",
      "markText": "可是穷人——他为什么需要诗歌，需要绘画，需要那种不适合唱歌跳舞的音乐呢？这些东西不能帮他收获庄稼或让他的孩子们身上多一件衣服。可他不管不顾，仍在坚持，也许他有他的理由，只是那些理由经不起审视。",
      "totalCount": 882,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300144647&chapterUid=71&rangeStart=1465&rangeEnd=1561",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fc332560813ab9f00g0174d0?chapterUid=71&rangeStart=1465&rangeEnd=1561"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300144647_73_931-963",
      "chapterUid": 73,
      "range": "931-963",
      "markText": "没有事件作为支柱，时间将无所依附。从虚无到虚无的压根就不是时光。",
      "totalCount": 845,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300144647&chapterUid=73&rangeStart=931&rangeEnd=963",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fc332560813ab9f00g0174d0?chapterUid=73&rangeStart=931&rangeEnd=963"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300144647_77_19082-19113",
      "chapterUid": 77,
      "range": "19082-19113",
      "markText": "查尔斯突然笑了。“那个可怜的杂种。”他说，他掀开毯子迎接了她。",
      "totalCount": 830,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300144647&chapterUid=77&rangeStart=19082&rangeEnd=19113",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fc332560813ab9f00g0174d0?chapterUid=77&rangeStart=19082&rangeEnd=19113"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300144647_118_15348-15401",
      "chapterUid": 118,
      "range": "15348-15401",
      "markText": "要是你能给我——嗯，就像你弟弟一样——能让我为他做的事感到骄傲，为他的进步感到欣慰，那我不知道会有多开心。",
      "totalCount": 800,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300144647&chapterUid=118&rangeStart=15348&rangeEnd=15401",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fc332560813ab9f00g0174d0?chapterUid=118&rangeStart=15348&rangeEnd=15401"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300144647_77_9075-9126",
      "chapterUid": 77,
      "range": "9075-9126",
      "markText": "“你知道我在想什么吗？我在想，在你漂亮的外表之下，你比我更刻薄，我还不及你的一半呢。我看你就是魔鬼。”",
      "totalCount": 799,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300144647&chapterUid=77&rangeStart=9075&rangeEnd=9126",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fc332560813ab9f00g0174d0?chapterUid=77&rangeStart=9075&rangeEnd=9126"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300144647_69_13365-13463",
      "chapterUid": 69,
      "range": "13365-13463",
      "markText": "查尔斯什么都不怕，所以他永远学不会勇敢。除了自己的事，他什么都不知道，所以他永远无法理解我刚刚跟你解释的那些话。把他送进军队，就是把他身上本该约束的东西放松了，可它们是不能放松的。我不敢让他走。”",
      "totalCount": 767,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300144647&chapterUid=69&rangeStart=13365&rangeEnd=13463",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fc332560813ab9f00g0174d0?chapterUid=69&rangeStart=13365&rangeEnd=13463"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300144647_68_4127-4178",
      "chapterUid": 68,
      "range": "4127-4178",
      "markText": "她这一生勇敢地承受磨难，从不抱怨，她坚信，那是她的上帝希望每个人都有的生活方式。她认为人会苦尽甘来的。",
      "totalCount": 741,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300144647&chapterUid=68&rangeStart=4127&rangeEnd=4178",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fc332560813ab9f00g0174d0?chapterUid=68&rangeStart=4127&rangeEnd=4178"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300144647_69_1470-1500",
      "chapterUid": 69,
      "range": "1470-1500",
      "markText": "等他回到康涅狄格州的家里时，剩下的病毒只够传染给他的妻子了。",
      "totalCount": 720,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300144647&chapterUid=69&rangeStart=1470&rangeEnd=1500",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fc332560813ab9f00g0174d0?chapterUid=69&rangeStart=1470&rangeEnd=1500"
    },
    {
